## Project Structure
```
php-social-messenger/
├── config/              # Database & app configuration
├── src/
│   ├── Core/            # Database, Session, Validator
│   ├── Models/          # User, Message, BlockedUser
│   └── Controllers/     # Auth, Chat, User, Contact
├── public/              # Front controller & assets
├── views/               # PHP view templates
└── database/            # SQL schema & seeds
```

## Files Created

### Core Components
- [Database.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/src/Core/Database.php) - PDO-based singleton with prepared statements
- [Session.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/src/Core/Session.php) - Secure session management with CSRF
- [Validator.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/src/Core/Validator.php) - Input validation & XSS prevention

### Models
- [User.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/src/Models/User.php) - Registration, login, profile management
- [Message.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/src/Models/Message.php) - CRUD operations for messages
- [BlockedUser.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/src/Models/BlockedUser.php) - Block/unblock functionality

### Controllers
- [AuthController.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/src/Controllers/AuthController.php) - Login, signup, logout
- [ChatController.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/src/Controllers/ChatController.php) - Messaging operations
- [UserController.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/src/Controllers/UserController.php) - Profile management
- [ContactController.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/src/Controllers/ContactController.php) - Contact list

### Views
- [login.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/views/auth/login.php), [signup.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/views/auth/signup.php) - Auth pages
- [index.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/views/chat/index.php) - Contacts list
- [conversation.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/chat%20app/php-social-messenger/views/chat/conversation.php) - Chat interface

## Next Steps

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Before using the application, you must set up the database.

```bash
# Create database and tables
mysql -u root -p < database/schema.sql

# Load demo data (optional)
mysql -u root -p social_messenger < database/seed.sql
```

